### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:23900
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Login to get JWT Token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "usuario": "admin",
  "senha": "admin123"
}

### Capture token from login response
@authToken = {{login.response.body.dados.token}}

### 2. Create Post with success (Valid Base64 image and simple letters-only caption)
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "imagem": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "legenda": "Meu primeiro post com legenda valida"
}

### 3. Create Post with invalid caption (contains numbers) - Should fail with dados_invalidos
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "imagem": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "legenda": "Post 123 invalido"
}

### 4. Create Post with invalid caption (contains accents) - Should fail with dados_invalidos
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "imagem": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "legenda": "Post acentuado nao pode"
}

### 5. Create Post with invalid image format - Should fail with dados_invalidos
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "imagem": "SGVsbG8gV29ybGQ=",
  "legenda": "Post imagem invalida"
}

### 6. List Posts for user 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 7. Like Post (Toggles Curtida -> Active)
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. List Posts for user 1 again to verify curtidas count is 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Unlike Post (Toggles Curtida -> Removed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 10. Update Post Caption with success
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "legenda": "Minha legenda atualizada"
}

### 11. Delete Post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
